data.description: Spacious and Roomy.  This is a large two-story home in the heart of town filled with abundant natural light. The house boasts four large bedrooms, three bathrooms, a big living room with built-in cabinets, a delightful family room with a fireplace, first floor laundry, heat pump with central air, and a full basement equipped with a basement dry system and high ceilings. The house was recently updated with new vinyl windows to ensure energy efficiency.   It is located just steps away from the popular Rails to Trails and various restaurants and stores.    PRICED TO SELL FAST.  CALL DOUG WERTZ FOR A TOUR 570-713-9961
